msgid "Reviewed by Sam Dawson"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "who_am_i"
msgid ""
"I’m a digital privacy and cybersecurity expert with over half a decade worth of experience reviewing privacy products. My research in academia included speculative execution attacks and AI-based "
"hacking simulations. My privacy work appears in TechRadar, CNET, and ITPro, in addition to a previous stint at ProPrivacy as their in-house technical researcher for VPNs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "lede_text"
msgid ""
"The Tapo C225 is one of TP-Link's AI-enabled home cameras, coming with a wide range of smart home features. It does everything from turning your lights off when you leave the house to sending you an"
" email notification if the water in one of your appliances starts leaking. It is, frankly, a very impressive piece of technology. It also has the potential to be immensely invasive, especially "
"considering TP-Link’s ties to the Chinese government."
msgstr ""
